HEADWORD: Lagenophera
<hw>Lagenophera</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A small genus of herbs of
Australia and South America having small solidary white or purple
flowers similar to true daisies of genus <gen>Bellis</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Lagenophera</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
